      "content": "thanks for that. those are solid foundational points. can you expand more on the economic side of the argument? my students need to be able to argue how stricter enforcement and border control actually benefit the domestic labor market and the broader economy, rather than just focusing on security. give me the most sophisticated version of that economic defense.",
